ZH: 我需要寄一封信，请问附近有邮政局吗？
EN: I need to send a letter, is there a post office nearby?

ZH: 每天下午五点前寄出的邮件会在第二天送达。
EN: The mails sent before 5 p.m. every afternoon will be delivered the next day.

ZH: 请您把这个包裹寄给我的父母，他们在北京。
EN: Could you please send this package to my parents? They are in Beijing.

ZH: 他通过邮政寄出了一张明信片，希望能收到朋友的回复。
EN: He sent a postcard through the mail and hopes to receive his friend's reply.

ZH: 我从网上购买了一本书，正在等待邮政送达。
EN: I bought a book online and am waiting for it to be delivered by the post office.

ZH: 邮政服务提供快递和平邮两种寄送选择。
EN: The postal service offers two types of delivery options: express delivery and ordinary mail.

ZH: 我收到了一封来自邮政的关于包裹丢失的通知。
EN: I received a notice from the post office regarding the loss of a package.

ZH: 这本书上的邮政编码可能不正确，请再核实一下。
EN: The postal code on this book might be incorrect, please double-check it.

ZH: 我需要购买一些邮资票才能寄出这些明信片。
EN: I need to buy some postage stamps to send these postcards.

ZH: 收件人的地址填写不完整，导致邮件无法发送。
EN: The recipient's address is incomplete, causing the mail to be undeliverable.

ZH: 请在信封上写上发件人的信息，方便邮局送达时联系。
EN: Please write the sender's information on the envelope, so the post office can contact you upon delivery.

ZH: 这个包裹需要通过航空邮政寄送。
EN: This package needs to be sent through airmail.

ZH: 邮政员提醒我寄出的邮件需要付费到我们这里。
EN: The postman reminded me that the mail I sent needs to be paid for upon delivery.

ZH: 邮政的快递服务很高效，一般情况下都能按时送达。
EN: The postal express service is efficient and generally delivers on time.

ZH: 请您帮我称一下这个包裹，我要填写邮局的快递单。
EN: Could you please weigh this package for me? I need to fill out the postal express form.

ZH: 这个包裹的收货地址填错了，需要更改一下。
EN: The shipping address for this package is filled out incorrectly and needs to be changed.

ZH: 你可以使用邮政储蓄银行进行存款和取款。
EN: You can make deposits and withdrawals using the postal savings bank.

ZH: 他刚刚收到了一封重要文件，是通过特快邮政寄来的。
EN: He just received an important document sent by express mail.

ZH: 邮政提供了线上查询服务，可以实时查看邮件的寄送信息。
EN: The post office provides an online tracking service where you can check the delivery status of your mail in real-time.

ZH: 我将用邮政寄送一些明信片给我的外国朋友。
EN: I will send some postcards to my foreign friends through the postal service.
